subject: Horse Racing
Breeders' Cup (Horse Races)
Jockeys, Drivers and Trainers
lead_paragraph: Shanghai Bobby, undefeated in five starts, held off He’s Had Enough to win the Juvenile and allow Rosie Napravnik to join Julie Krone as the only female jockeys to win Breeders’ Cup races.
